U.K. stocks recouped losses,
leaving the benchmark FTSE 100 Index little changed. The gauge
slid 0.1 percent to 5,630.77 as of 9:12 a.m. in  London , having
earlier fallen as much as 0.6 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
